    "faq_iRUrfY": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_pqJFRj": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How are Grüns Kids different than Grüns Adults?",
            "row_content": "<p>Our Grüns Kids has the same amazing ingredients but are properly dosed for ages 2-13 and have a smaller serving size of delicious gummy bears (15 g in Kids vs. 20 g in Adults)<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_PMk9G9": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long does it take for the gummies to arrive?",
            "row_content": "<p>We're fast! Orders typically ship within 24 hours and, on average, arrive 2 days later. So, in just 3 days, your kids could be snacking on these delicious gummies and enjoying improved health.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_bTfcd3": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What's inside each order?",
            "row_content": "<p>Our gummies come in a spacious 8.5\" x 10\" pouch with 28 daily sachets—a sachet is just a fancy term for a snack pack! Each snack pack contains a small handful of gummy bears, perfect for your child to enjoy daily. You’ll receive 28 daily snack packs within that larger pouch. We highly recommend setting up a subscription. Not only do you get better pricing, but it ensures that your child will always have their favorite gummies on hand, helping to keep their healthy habits on track!<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_DK8KPF": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "When should I expect my child to feel the benefits of Grüns?",
            "row_content": "<p>The timeline for experiencing the benefits of Grüns can vary from person to person. Some individuals may notice improvements within days or weeks, while others may gradually experience them. Consistent daily use is essential for the best results.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_rh6pb6": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What ages are Grüns Kids recommended for?",
            "row_content": "<p>Grüns Kids are recommended for ages 2-13 years old and are appropriately dosed to have a smaller serving size of delicious gummy bears!<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_xycyCr": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Are Grüns Kids free from major allergens?",
            "row_content": "<p>Grüns are gluten-free, dairy-free, nut-free, soy-free, and vegan. They contain no synthetic sweeteners, no synthetic dyes, or gelatin and most of our ingredients are organic. You can view a full list of allergens Grüns is free from here<br/><a href=\"https://gruns.co/pages/science\" target=\"_blank\">:<span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">https://gruns.co/pages/science</span></a></p>"
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_67p3kw": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What if my child isn’t happy with Grüns?",
            "row_content": "<p>We want you and your child to have the best experience with Grüns. We offer a 30-day guarantee on your first order so you can try Grüns risk-free! If your kiddo isn’t loving Grüns, you can start a return or exchange for your first order through our self-service portal: <a href=\"https://gruns.loopreturns.com/#/\">https://gruns.loopreturns.com/#/</a>.</p><p>A few reminders:</p><ul><li>Returns are only accepted on first-time purchases. Exchanges are available on repeat purchases.</li><li>All returns have a $5 handling fee, and shipping costs aren’t refunded. Exchanges are totally free!</li><li>If you’re subscribed, you'll need to cancel your subscription separately. <a href=\"https://gruns.co/policies/refund-policy\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">See Terms & Conditions.</span></a><br/></li></ul><p>Have questions or need help outside of your first order? We're happy to chat—reach out at <a href=\"mailto:support@gruns.co\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">support@gruns.co</span>| Opens Email</a>.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
